The pdfTeX team is happy to announce the release of a new RC version:

===========================================================================
                               pdfTeX 1.40.8-rc1
===========================================================================

This is the announcement of pdfTeX 1.40.8-rc1, an extended version of TeX that
can create PDF directly from TeX source files and enhance the result of TeX
typesetting with the help of PDF.

===========================================================================
  Main changes of pdfTeX 1.40.8-rc1
===========================================================================

- Incorporated synctex
- Incorporated the new version of TeX: 3.1415926
- The pool file is now compiled in
- some bugfixes

For complete release notes see http://www.pdftex.org/NEWS

